  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网边缘处理的流程图。核心是从TelemetryStream开始，经过PLC逻辑处理，再到MQTT Broker分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，TelemetryStream作为起点。PLC逻辑是A1节点对吧？那MQTT Broker是T1还是D1？我看到您描述里有两个不同的Broker角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "T1",
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "T1是工具层的MQTT Broker，用于内部转发；D1是决策点，判断是否需要走ActuatorController路径。这两个要分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "D1",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把U节点设为TelemetryStream，用user样式。A1作为PLC Logic，走assistant样式。T1作为工具层Broker，走tool样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1",
        "T1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，还需要一个H1节点，也是TelemetryStream，作为Assistant的上下文输入。它直接连到A1，不走U那条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H1",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加H1，同样标记为tool样式。现在U→A1，H1→A1，A1→T1→A1形成循环。接下来处理D1决策点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H1",
        "U",
        "A1",
        "T1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，D1判断是否需要触发ActuatorController。如果Yes，走C1然后回到U；如果No，进入A2的备用PLC Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "A2",
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "D1设为decision样式，C1是assistant样式。D1-Yes→C1→U，D1-No→A2。A2也是assistant样式对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "A2",
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的。A2之后要检查D2，判断是否需要EdgeNode处理。这里有个分支：Yes走R1到APPD，No直接到AT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A2",
        "D2",
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "R1是MQTT Broker吗？APPD我看命名像是App相关的节点，应该走app样式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R1",
        "APPD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，R1是Broker走assistant样式，APPD是App执行节点走app样式。APPD之后还要连到AT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加D2决策点、R1、APPD。D2-Yes→R1→APPD→AT。D2-No直接到AT。AT是什么类型？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D2",
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "AT是最终的MQTT Broker，assistant样式。从AT分出两条路径：Needs App Execution走APP_ACK到U2，No Execution Needed直接到U2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "AT设好了。APP_ACK是app样式，U2是ActuatorController，user样式。两条线都汇聚到U2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整体结构差不多了。帮我检查一下样式分类：U和U2是user，A1/A2/C1/R1/AT是assistant，D1/D2是decision，APPD/APP_ACK是app，T1/H1是tool。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "U2",
        "A1",
        "A2",
        "C1",
        "R1",
        "AT",
        "D1",
        "D2",
        "APPD",
        "APP_ACK",
        "T1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "发现个问题：class定义里有R2和CALL，但流程图里没用到这两个节点。需要删掉吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R2",
        "CALL"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "对，那是之前草稿的残留。删掉R2和CALL。另外确认下APPD的命名，应该是AppD还是APPD？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已清理R2和CALL。APPD保持大写，表示App Deployment节点。现在class定义是：user含U/U2，assistant含A1/A2/C1/R1/AT，decision含D1/D2，app含APPD/APP_ACK，tool含T1/H1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD",
        "APP_ACK",
        "class definitions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，A1到T1再到A1这个循环，箭头方向对吗？应该是A1输出到T1，T1处理后返回A1？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "T1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "当前是A1→T1和T1→A1两条线，形成双向。需要改成单向循环A1→T1→A1吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "T1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，应该是A1→T1→A1的串联，不是双向。T1处理后把数据给回A1，然后A1再输出到D1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "T1",
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正：A1→T1→A1串联，然后A1→D1。这样T1作为工具节点在A1的处理循环中。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "T1",
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看D2的分支，R1→APPD→AT这条线，APPD是PLC Logic类型吗？命名有点混淆。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "APPD显示为IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，但样式是app。这是App层的PLC逻辑，和A1/A2的底层PLC Logic区分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD",
        "A1",
        "A2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，APPD是应用层部署的PLC逻辑，A1/A2是边缘硬件的PLC。AT之后到U2的两条路径标签确认下：Needs App Execution和No Execution Needed。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPD",
        "AT",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "标签已标注。AT→Needs App Execution→APP_ACK→U2，AT→No Execution Needed→U2。完整路径通了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 27,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后确认下H1的定位：它是Assistant的上下文输入，和U同类型但走不同路径。H1→A1直接触发，不经过U的用户交互层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H1",
